article.description: Darius Graham scored 19 points and had five assists, Siler Schneider scored 16 points off the bench and UC Davis beat Northern Arizona 89-76 on Sunday.
article.headline: Graham scores 19; UC Davis beats Northern Arizona 89-76
article.linkText: Graham scores 19; UC Davis beats Northern Arizona 89-76
article.story: SANTA CLARA, Calif. -- Darius Graham scored 19 points and had five assists, Siler Schneider scored 16 points off the bench and UC Davis beat Northern Arizona 89-76 on Sunday. Graham hit two 3-pointers and a jumper amid a 27-9 run the Aggies (2-1) used to pull away to a 47-23 halftime lead. Graham hit three more 3s in the second half and the Lumberjacks (0-3) got no closer than 11 the rest of the way. Chima Moneke and Mikey Henn each scored 11 points off the bench, and J.T. Adenrele grabbed three offensive boards. The Aggies shot 13 of 25 (52 percent) from long distance and 53 percent (32 of 60) from the floor while holding the Lumberjacks to 27 of 66 (41 percent). Northern Arizona's Jaleni Neely scored 24 points, Ako Kaluna had 17 (13 in the first half), Mike Green scored 16 and Marcus DeBerry added 13.
